<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Response to Your Request</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #111827; line-height: 1.6;">
    <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= userName %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Regarding your request (<strong><%= ticketId %></strong>) about "<%= subject %>":</p>
      <div style="background:#f9fafb; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px; padding:16px; margin:12px 0; white-space:pre-wrap;"><%= replyMessage %></div>
      <p>If you have more questions, just reply to this email and our team will assist you.</p>
      <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 20px 0;" />
      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">
        <strong><%= companyName %></strong><br/>
        <%= companyAddress %><br/>
        Need help? Email us at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #2563eb;"><%= supportEmail %></a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
  </html>


